</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>eBay shipping conditions</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the terms for the shipping profile in the <strong>eBay shipping conditions</strong> tab.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>eBay return policy</strong></p></td>
