</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Do not accept the following purchasers</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to exclude certain purchasers.<br>
<strong>Activate</strong> = Buyers must meet this requirement or they are excluded.<br>
