<h2 id="2300">4. Preparing listings</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Listings</strong> to carry out the settings for all listings regardless of the market. In order to create listings in plentymarkets, you must carry out the following settings and have created your <a href="/en/item/managing-items#20">items</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2400">4.1. Carrying out the basic settings</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The settings in the <strong>System » Listings » Settings</strong> menu apply to all listings.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out the basic settings for listings:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Listings » Settings</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as described in <a href="#basic-settings-listings">Table 13</a> below.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
