<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Create new market listing</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select whether an error message should be shown if there is already a listing for this item or whether the system should not check for duplicate market listings.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item name column for the listing title</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select <strong>Name 1</strong>, <strong>Name 2</strong> or <strong>Name 3</strong>. This item name is transferred. Item names are entered in the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#50">texts</a> tab of the item.</p></td>
