<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2600">4.3. Setting up the checkout process</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out the settings for the listings' checkout in the <strong>System » Listings » Checkout</strong> menu.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Setting up the checkout:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Listings » Checkout</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as described in <a href="#settings-checkout">Table 15</a> below.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
