<i class="fa icon-important" title="Important"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Activate the option Wildcard character in layout template (eBay)</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you use template variables which contain properties, such as <strong>&#123;&#37; GetItemPropertyById() &#37;&#125;</strong> and <strong>&#123;&#37; GetItemPropertyByName() &#37;&#125;</strong>, you have to activate the option <strong>Wildcard character in layout template (eBay)</strong> for the selected property, so that the property is displayed in the layout template. This is done in the <strong>System » Item » Properties</strong> menu.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
