</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings as described in <a href="#ebay-importing-listings">Table 46</a> below.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Sync</strong> to import the eBay listings.<br>
→ A new section is displayed where you can see the processing status.</p>
