<h3 id="11400">22.2. Uploading listings to international eBay platforms</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In this chapter, you will learn how to set up listings in order to upload items with translated item descriptions directly to international eBay platforms. You can use your existing eBay member account for creating offers for other platforms. Carry out country-specific settings, e.g. prices in a different currency or item data in a different language.</p>
</div>
